snippet.title: Snake O Tron Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Epic MegaJam 2023 Entry.

In a near future where AI rule the world, humans has only one thing left for a better future and it is to win the "Snake-O-Tron" and hope to have a land free of AI. But everyone wants it.

This is where your journey begins...

This is a game mixed with Snake in 3D with a Tron Style where the goal is to pickup energy ball. Beware of your own tail or the solar bombs dropping from the zeppelins above. 

@UnrealEngine
